*** INSTALLATION AND CONFIGURATION OF SQLMesh
 - using VSCODE  run the following command
 
 
 First, create the virtual environment:
	python -m venv .env
Then activate it:
	source .env/bin/activate
For windows 
 .env\Scripts\Activate.ps1
 
 
 Install the core SQLMesh library with pip
	pip install sqlmesh

In this example, we specify the duckdb dialect: - this will create config-yaml file for further configuration.

	sqlmesh init duckdb
